Here's a [direct link](https://ci.tensorflow.org/view/Nightly/job/nightly-matrix-android/TF_BUILD_CONTAINER_TYPE=ANDROID,TF_BUILD_IS_OPT=OPT,TF_BUILD_IS_PIP=NO_PIP,TF_BUILD_PYTHON_VERSION=PYTHON2,label=android-slave/lastSuccessfulBuild/artifact/bazel-out/local_linux/bin/tensorflow/examples/android/tensorflow_demo.apk) to the latest APK.
